Add RoundMenuMainWindow implementation for circular rotating menu demo
- Introduced a new class `RoundMenuMainWindow` to demonstrate the functionality of the `RoundMenuWidget`. - Implemented UI setup with controls for adding, removing, and clearing menu items. - Added color customization options for the center button, menu items, and hover effects. - Included options for displaying background, separator lines, and enabling rotation animations. - Integrated presets for different menu styles: classic, cool, and minimalist. - Connected signals and slots for interactive behavior of the menu and controls. - Set up demo menu items with icons and tooltips for user interaction.
